{
  "stem": "13874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember when he was brought back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we finally were allowed to go back to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure he died-- not easily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Swill.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Swill, what you feed the pigs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had every three days, two shared a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And three times a day we had to go to the kitchen, got big buckets of coffee and mostly tapioca.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the evening it was stew, as I described already before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, talking about what we were fed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That friend of mine, Ernst Thingfelder, he was strictly orthodox kosher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He recoiled of eating that stews, which was everything together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I gave him most of my bread, and I ate the meat-- for he wouldn't touch the meat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I practically didn't eat any bread there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we both got out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were you in the barracks with him, the same barracks?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in the same barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started out with 200.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Originally the barracks held 300.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as I said-- I'm talking about our room alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you want to talk about the barracks, you multiply it by four.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were pushed in, as I said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later as more and more were released, it was just at the day when I was released, they started to reconvert the barracks to the original bunks, which held 52 people per room.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Before that, we actually dwindled down from 200 to 100 and more.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were lucky, we had a few more blankets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had a little more room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have to sleep practically on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lights out and you shut up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The big question was, why?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
